Text: So after downloading this, I've come to the conclusion that she only released a total of 5 songs - but she released them 12 ways across 8 CDs.

You have:

Acoustic
Acoustic Live
Remix
Studio Version
Live Remix
Acoustic Remix
Acoustic Live Remix

Whatever happened to artists releasing just one version of their song (maybe 2 as I do agree that an acoustic version is legit) and that's it?
